            <offset>0</offset>
            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>﻿Case 1 was referred to our department at 14 months of age due to short stature and his dysmorphic features.</text>
                <annotation id="1">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0004322</infon>
                    <location length="13" offset="66"/>
                    <text>short stature</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>109</offset>
                <text>He was born to consanguineous parents at 39 weeks of gestation.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>173</offset>
                <text>His birth weight, height and head circumference were 2,500 g (−1.68 standard deviation score (SDS)), 45 cm (−1.85 SDS), and 35 cm (−0.42 SDS), respectively (Gokcay, Furman, &amp; Neyzi, 2008).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>363</offset>
                <text>On physical examination, his weight, height, and head circumference were 4,410 g (−4.28 SDS), 61.5 cm (−4.82 SDS), and 43 cm (−1.03 SDS), respectively.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>515</offset>
                <text>He was noted to have a triangular face, frontal bossing, depressed nasal bridge, fleshy, upturned nose, anteverted nares and a pointed, prominent chin.</text>
                <annotation id="2">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000325</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="23"/>
                    <text>triangular face</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="3">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0002007</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="40"/>
                    <text>frontal bossing</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="4">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0005280</infon>
                    <location length="22" offset="57"/>
                    <text>depressed nasal bridge</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="5">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <location length="6" offset="81"/>
                    <text>fleshy</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="8">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000463</infon>
                    <location length="13" offset="89"/>
                    <text>upturned nose</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="7">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <location length="4" offset="98"/>
                    <text>nose</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="9">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000463</infon>
                    <location length="16" offset="104"/>
                    <text>anteverted nares</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="10">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <location length="7" offset="127"/>
                    <text>pointed</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="13">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0000303</infon>
                    <location length="14" offset="136"/>
                    <text>prominent chin</text>
